2002;;The Importance of Being Earnest;;British;;Oliver Parker;;Rupert Everett, Colin Firth, Judi Dench;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Importance_of_Being_Earnest_(2002_film);;In this adaptation of Oscar Wilde's play about mistaken identities, two gentlemen in 1890s London use the same pseudonym, Ernest, for their secret courtship activities. Chaos ensues when both men find themselves face-to-face and have to explain who they really are.